The format of the simulation.data files is as follows:
number of piles
height of pile 1
x center of pile 1
y center of pile 1
x extent of pile 1
y extent of pile 1
height of pile 2
x center of pile 2
...
x extent of last pile
y extent of last pile
maximum number of time steps for the simulation
maximum simulation time for the simulation
how often to output the visualization data (time steps per output)
adapt flag (0 no, 1 yes)
visualization output type (mshplot, tecplot, pady's output)
GIS information main directory
GIS sub-directory
GIS mapset
GIS map

